#   Default [/healthz]
#
# [*verbosity*]
#   Set log verbosity
#   Defaults to 2
#
# [*log_dir*]
#   If non-empty, write log files in this directory
#
# [*log_file*]
#   If non-empty, use this log file
#
# [*log_file_max_size*]
